    public interface ComponentImplementingClassesLink
extends EObject
    A representation of the model object ' Component Implementing Classes Link'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Composite Component
    • Component
    • Implementing Classes
    • Sub Components
    • Provided Interfaces
    • Required Interfaces
    • Is Initial Component
